{\it Discussion: } To summarize, the numerical evidence clearly points to a plaquette ground state for the SU(6) model on the honeycomb lattice, but 
with a chiral phase close by in parameter space. Even if it led to the wrong conclusion, the mean-field approach should be given credit for identifying
the right candidates with very similar energies.\cite{SzirmaiG2011} This lends further support to the mean-field prediction by 
